willing to be transformational,

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:31.440
to break out of the tunnel
vision of thinking narrowly

00:03:31.440 --> 00:03:34.920
about one's interests and
the myopia of focusing

00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:38.250
