00:09:39.900 --> 00:09:42.700
We had a panel with Senator Ben
Cardin and a number of other people

00:09:42.700 --> 00:09:44.120
over at the Holocaust Museum.

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:46.350
And I also have been
doing a lot of work lately

00:09:46.350 --> 00:09:48.750
in a very immediate
sense on issues in Syria.

00:09:48.750 --> 00:09:52.420
And those can be rather
