by friends and colleagues

00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:57.200
who were all broken up about this.

00:20:57.200 --> 00:21:01.020
But when I went down to the
square where he had been killed

00:21:01.020 --> 00:21:05.090
and I saw 16-year-olds lighting
candles and playing guitars

00:21:05.090 --> 00:21:08.670
for this gruff old guy who didn't
have Kennedy-esque charisma,

00:21:08.670 --> 00:21:11.480
it really affected me
even more profoundly

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.030
than my own friends and colleagues.

00:21:13.030 --> 00:21:17.380
And so some ways charisma is a
product, and ultimately you see it,

00:21:17.380 --> 00:21:19.450
but it's not the kind
of thing that, you know,

00:21:19.450 --> 00:21:21.450
sort of consultants
and others look for.

00:21:21.450 --> 00:21:25.100
We also get into some
negative qualities,

00:21:25.100 --> 00:21:28.730
because the point here is
admiration, but not hero worship.

00:21:28.730 --> 00:21:31.500
And the point being many
imperfect people can be very

00:21:31.500 --> 00:21:32.960
effective statesmen.

00:21:32.960 --> 00:21:37.300
Political skills of a variety
of kind also were important

00:21:37.300 --> 00:21:40.540
in terms of these two profiles.

00:21:40.540 --> 00:21:43.780
Why really gets into the
vision, why did these

00:21:43.780 --> 00:21:47.000
and others develop their guiding
visions beyond the way the world is

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:48.780
to how it could be?

00:21:48.780 --> 00:21:51.240
Being able and willing to
push beyond standard analysis

00:21:51.240 --> 00:21:53.990
and see the need for
profound change was a key.

00:21:53.990 --> 00:21:56.060 position:56%
What was the basis for that insight?

00:21:56.060 --> 00:21:58.070
I looked for turning
points, decisive moments

00:21:58.070 --> 00:21:59.780
when key choices were
made, and ideas

00:21:59.780 --> 00:22:02.140
and strategies started to develop.

00:22:02.140 --> 00:22:04.890
A vision is really a
story, a political one.

00:22:04.890 --> 00:22:07.600
It's akin in form and functions
to what we think of more broadly

00:22:07.600 --> 00:22:10.880
as narratives that provide the
why for the transformation.

00:22:10.880 --> 00:22:13.010
And while it varies
in different cases,

00:22:13.010 --> 00:22:15.430
you'll find that it
always has three elements.

00:22:15.430 --> 00:22:16.730
